snippet.textDisplay: I am very familiar with Nin and Klye in the DissociaDID system, but the system's Littles are very, very rarely shown in the system's videos, for very good protective reasons. It was a very special thing to be able to hear one of the system's littles talk, but, dang, I sure felt very mamma bear about him/her fronting and not knowing what was going on. Thank you for being gentle, kind, and understanding with him/her. And, yeah, it absolutely tore me up to see him/her crying. But he/she was crying for a good reason, because he/she didn't feel alone anymore, so I'm happy for that. Also, thanks for letting us know about the other systems; I wasn't familiar with them.

snippet.textDisplay:
Okay let's just stop for a minute and appreciate the person Anthony is and what he has become thorought this years. One of the pioneers of youtube comedy, one of the most professional youtubers, he takes his work so seriously yet it seems to be so natural for him, and now his is doing this amazing project.
One of the things I hate the most in some of these projects of knowing marginalized or misunderstood society members, is the way the host acts like "look I'm going to spend a day with this weird-ass people to show everyone how weird they are and prove to everybody that they're crazy so we make fun of them". And I'm SO happy to see the complete opposite happening here. I'm really proud to see the person he has become. So beautiful to watch.

snippet.textDisplay:
What one of the girls said when explaining the disorder (Sorry dont remember her name)

That kinda hit close to home, the amnesia thing because I can’t remember anything from the ages of 1-4, only really the ages of 6-10, I can remember most of the memories from ages 7-10 definitely because I think thats when my parents split and things got calmer, 6 is more fuzzy.

I don’t know, maybe it was just because I was dropped as a baby and my brain just did a full 180.

I don’t think I have DID at all, I’ve never just switched personalities and etc, I’ve just switched moods from one being loving and calm to a angry crackhead, I am not self diagnosing that I think I do, doing that is majorly dumb, I’m just saying that one thing hit close to home.

Aw, the little child alter, It makes my mother instinct kick in and want to take care of them, thats such a good and cute and wise who has so much idea of this and what to say and just a happy kid, I want hold them and just LOVE THEM, I relate to kyle so hard just “goddamnit nin why you put us in a skirt” its just a male/or whatever in a girl body and its funny because he/they understands this is what girls like and its what looks good on a girl body but its just like a tomboy being in a pink and frilly dress lmaooo, and he/they tied his/their hair back and was cussing like hell and they/he was like “bro that shit makes me mad.” Just acting like a total homie.

Its like a guy on guy convo but just a guy/or whatever in a girl’s body, like if you switched bodies with a guy.

But its so scary to think people can take advantage of this, like if your child alter kicks in to think a grown bad person will take advantage of a grown women whos over 18’s body so technically it isn’t pedophillia when it comes to age and body circumstances, but now has the mind of a literal child and the oblivious attitude of a child, that’s terrifying.
